aff.html#nt=byline" class="trb_bylines_nm_au_a">Mariel Garza</a></span          ></span    ><span class="trb_bylines_b"></span      ><a class="trb_bylines_cl" href="mailto:mariel.garza@latimes.com?subject=Regarding: &quot;&apos;Mission accomplished&apos; in recapture of Mexican drug kingpin &apos;El Chapo&apos; -- but for how long?&quot;" data-role="sc_sEmail">Contact Reporter</a    ></div  ></div>                            <ul class="trb_article_relatedTopics"    ><li class="trb_article_relatedTopics_li">              <a class="trb_article_relatedTopics_a" title="Mexico"                href="/topic/international/mexico-PLGEO00000613-topic.html#nt=taxonomy-article"> Mexico</a></li>            <li class="trb_article_relatedTopics_li">              <a class="trb_article_relatedTopics_a" title="Joaquin Guzman"                href="/topic/crime-law-justice/organized-crime/joaquin-guzman-PEOCVC00347-topic.html#nt=taxonomy-article"> Joaquin Guzman</a></li>            <li class="trb_article_relatedTopics_li">              <a class="trb_article_relatedTopics_a" title="Donald Trump"                href="http://www.latimes.com/projects/la-na-all-things-trump"> Donald Trump</a></li>            <li class="trb_article_relatedTopics_li">              <a class="trb_article_relatedTopics_a" title="Joe Arpaio"                href="/topic/crime-law-justice/law-enforcement/joe-arpaio-PEPLT00008676-topic.html#nt=taxonomy-article"> Joe Arpaio</a></li></ul>  <div class="trb_gptAd" data-role="adloader adloader_ad delayload delayload_done" data-adloader-size="300x250" data-state="adloader_unloaded"  data-withinviewport-options="bottomOffset=100&topOffset=1000000"  data-adloader-position="articleCubeCombo" data-adloader-adtype="cubecombo" data-adloader-label ></div    >          <div class="trb_article_dateline"><time itemprop="datePublished" class="trb_article_dateline_time" data-dt="January 8, 2016, 1:20 PM" datetime="2016-01-08T13:20:00PST"></time>  </div>    </header>            <secti